#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:2
msgid "Add a cascading hydropower system"
msgstr "新增梯级水电系统"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:4
msgid ""
"**Goal.** Introduce a multi-station hydropower cascade (e.g. a new river "
"basin) into a scenario, with per-station reservoir physics and inter-"
"station water-delay routing."
msgstr "**目标。** 在算例中引入一个多站点的梯级水电系统 (如新的流域),包含按电站建立的水库物理过程和站间水流延迟路由。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is the heaviest \"add a tech\" recipe because hydropower stations "
"are first-class techs in PREP-SHOT (not aggregated). Each station is its "
"own row in ``tech_registry.csv`` AND has its own reservoir- parameter "
"rows across ~10 reservoir-specific files. See the shipped Lower Mekong "
"scenario (``examples/southeast_asia``, 57 stations) and the Thailand "
"scenario (``examples/thailand``, 13 stations) for fully-worked examples."
msgstr ""
"这是 \"新增技术\" 中最重的秘籍,因为在 PREP-SHOT 中每个水电站都是一等技术 (而非聚合在一起)。每个电站在 "
"``tech_registry.csv`` 中占一行,并在约 10 个水库相关文件中各占一行。完整示例可参阅随仓库提供的湄公河下游算例 "
"(``examples/southeast_asia``,57 个电站) 与泰国算例 (``examples/thailand``,13 "
"个电站)。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:17
msgid "Steps"
msgstr "步骤"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:19
msgid ""
"**1. Pick station slugs.** No spaces; dots stripped. Example for a "
"3-station cascade:"
msgstr "**1. 选定电站 slug。** 不允许空格,需去掉点号。一个 3 站梯级的例子:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:26
msgid "**2. Register each as a hydro tech.** In ``tech_registry.csv``:"
msgstr "**2. 将每个电站注册为水电技术。** 在 ``tech_registry.csv`` 中:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:35
msgid ""
"The ``carrier='hydro'`` is special-cased; the model loads the reservoir-"
"physics constraint stack for these techs."
msgstr "``carrier='hydro'`` 是特殊处理的;模型会为这些技术加载完整的水库物理约束。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:38
msgid "**3. Map each station to a zone.** In ``reservoir_zone.csv``:"
msgstr "**3. 将每个电站映射到区域。** 在 ``reservoir_zone.csv`` 中:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:47
msgid ""
"**4. Populate per-station reservoir parameters.** Each of these files "
"needs one row per station:"
msgstr "**4. 填写按电站的水库参数。** 以下文件每个电站各占一行:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:60
msgid ""
"**5. Time-varying inputs.** ``reservoir_inflow.csv`` needs an entry per "
"``(station, year, month, hour)``; same for ``reservoir_storage_max.csv`` "
"and ``reservoir_storage_min.csv`` (though these are usually constant "
"within a month). Endpoint volumes go in "
"``reservoir_initial_storage_level.csv`` and "
"``reservoir_final_storage_level.csv``."
msgstr ""
"**5. 随时间变化的输入。** ``reservoir_inflow.csv`` 需为每个 ``(station, year, month, "
"hour)`` 提供一行;``reservoir_storage_max.csv`` 与 "
"``reservoir_storage_min.csv`` 同理 (虽然这些通常在月内恒定)。期初/期末库容写入 "
"``reservoir_initial_storage_level.csv`` 与 "
"``reservoir_final_storage_level.csv``。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:67
msgid ""
"**6. Cascade routing.** Define water travel time between connected "
"stations in ``reservoir_water_delay_time.csv``:"
msgstr "**6. 梯级路由。** 在 ``reservoir_water_delay_time.csv`` 中定义相连电站之间的水流时间:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:76
msgid ""
"Delay is in hours. Stations with no downstream entry are terminal (water "
"leaves the modeled system)."
msgstr "延迟单位为小时。无下游条目的电站为末端 (水流离开建模系统)。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:79
msgid ""
"**7. Piecewise functions.** Two more files describe the non-linear "
"hydropower physics, both in long-format with per-station rows:"
msgstr "**7. 分段函数。** 还有两个文件用长格式按电站描述非线性水电物理:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:82
msgid ""
"``reservoir_forebay_level_volume_function.csv`` -- forebay elevation as a"
" function of reservoir volume."
msgstr ""

