msgid ""
"``reservoir_tailrace_level_discharge_function.csv`` -- tailrace elevation"
" as a function of total discharge."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:87
msgid "PREP-SHOT linearizes these inside the head-iteration loop."
msgstr "PREP-SHOT 在水头迭代循环中将其线性化。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:89
msgid ""
"**8. Existing capacity (optional).** If the cascade is partly already "
"built:"
msgstr "**8. 已有装机 (可选)。** 若梯级中部分电站已建成:"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:98
msgid ""
"**9. Per-tech files.** Don't forget the eight non-reservoir per-tech "
"files (lifetime, fuel_price, emission_factor, fixed_OM_cost, "
"variable_OM_cost, investment_cost, ramp_up, ramp_down) -- each station "
"needs a row, even if mostly zeros (no fuel, no emissions)."
msgstr ""
"**9. 按技术的文件。** 别忘了 8 个与水库无关的按技术索引文件 "
"(lifetime、fuel_price、emission_factor、fixed_OM_cost、variable_OM_cost、investment_cost、ramp_up、ramp_down)——每个电站都需一行,即便绝大多数为零"
" (无燃料、无排放)。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:104
msgid "Verify"
msgstr "验证"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:123
msgid "Common pitfalls"
msgstr "常见陷阱"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:125
msgid ""
"**Slug consistency.** The same station name must appear in every CSV that"
" mentions it: ``tech_registry``, ``reservoir_zone``, all the "
"``reservoir_*`` files, and the per-tech files. Mistyping one breaks the "
"load."
msgstr ""
"**slug 必须保持一致。** 同一个电站名必须出现在每个引用它的 CSV "
"中:``tech_registry``、``reservoir_zone``、所有 ``reservoir_*`` "
"文件以及按技术索引的文件。任何一处拼错都会导致加载失败。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:129
msgid ""
"**Cascade direction.** ``upstream_tech`` is always the station the water "
"leaves; ``downstream_tech`` is the next station downstream. Reversing "
"them silently produces nonsense."
msgstr ""
"**梯级方向。** ``upstream_tech`` 始终是水离开的那个电站;``downstream_tech`` "
"是其下游的下一个电站。颠倒这两列会静默地产生无意义的结果。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:132
msgid ""
"**Inflow data shape.** ``reservoir_inflow.csv`` is per-(station, year, "
"month, hour). With config ``hour=8760, month=1``, that's 8760 rows per "
"station -- big but unavoidable. Reduce hour count during development."
msgstr ""
"**入流数据形状。** ``reservoir_inflow.csv`` 按 (站、年、月、时) 索引。在 ``hour=8760, "
"month=1`` 配置下,每站为 8760 行——较大但不可避免。开发期间可减小 hour 数量。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:136
msgid ""
"**Constraints can make the model infeasible.** If "
"``reservoir_outflow_min`` exceeds ``reservoir_outflow_max`` at any "
"station, or if the demanded generation exceeds ``capacity_max`` for too "
"many hours, the LP will be reported infeasible by HiGHS with no slack "
"indication. Check your bounds."
msgstr ""
"**约束可能导致模型不可行。** 若任一电站的 ``reservoir_outflow_min`` 大于 "
"``reservoir_outflow_max``,或所需出力在过多小时数中超过 ``capacity_max``,HiGHS "
"会报告不可行,但不会给出松弛信息。请检查你的上下界。"

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:142
msgid ""
"Looking at ``examples/southeast_asia/input/`` is the fastest way to see "
"what a complete 57-station cascade dataset looks like."
msgstr "查看 ``examples/southeast_asia/input/`` 是了解完整 57 站梯级数据集长什么样的最快方法。"

